title: TV5Monde Secrets d Histoire Louis XIV l homme et le Roi PDTV x26
description:
Louis XIV, L'homme et le Roi

History Documentary hosted by Stephane Bern, published by TV5Monde broadcasted as part of TV5Monde Secrets d'Histoire series in 2015 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/6/6c/Louis-XIV-L-homme-et-le-Roi-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Stephane Bern discovers the fascinating life of the Sun King, his childhood, his taking power, his conception of the state and absolute monarchy by divine right and it embodies his many battles, loves and passion for the arts, architecture, gardens, music or dance...
